data.description: FOR SALE!  This farm style beauty checks ALL the boxes!!  *FINISHED BASEMENT, *INGROUND POOL, *4 YRS OLD,* LARGE 0.4 ACRE CUL-DE-SAC LOT, *POND VIEW, *SWAC SCHOOLS, *3.5 CAR GARAGE, *4 BEDS, *2 FULL BATHS, *2 HALF BATHS, *PLUS A DEN IN THE BASEMENT!   Enjoy your morning coffee on the 12x12 deck, before taking a dip in the heated pool that was installed along with the white vinyl fence in 2021.  You will love the 4' wide staircases, large foyer entry, Walk in closets, beautiful granite kitchen island, Massive 20x17 master bedroom ,and laundry on main level,  The garage layout and high ceilings have endless opportunities for hobbies or workshops.  This home is conveniently located close to I69, Jefferson pointe, Sweetwater sound, and Hwy 30.  Don't miss this opportunity!  Schedule your showing today!
